Path: README.md
...
    28	
    29	1. **Place Your Order**: Order on Thuisbezorgd.nl as usual
    30	2. **Open Extension**: Click the extension icon when your order exceeds budget
    31	3. **Calculate Split**: Click "Calculate Now" to see payment breakdown
    32	4. **View Details**: Click "Show Individual Payment Breakdown" for full details
    33	5. **Collect Payments**: Use generated Tikkie message to collect from team members
    34	
    35	## ⚙️ Settings
    36	
    37	Configure the extension to match your needs:
    38	
    39	- **Daily Budget**: Set your company's budget limit (default: €14 per person)
    40	- **Auto-calculate**: Enable automatic calculation when order pages load
