    13	- **Tikkie Payment Link**: Your personal Tikkie payment link (if provided)
    14	- **Preferences**: Auto-calculate settings and display preferences
    15	
    16	### Order Data (Temporary Processing Only)
    17	- **Participant Names**: Names from Thuisbezorgd order pages
    18	- **Order Amounts**: Individual order costs and fees
    19	- **Order Totals**: Subtotals, delivery fees, service fees, discounts
    20	
    21	**Important**: Order data is processed locally in your browser and is NOT stored permanently or transmitted to external servers.
    22	
    23	## How We Use Your Information
    24	
    25	### Local Processing
    26	- Split payment costs and calculate distributions
    27	- Display individual payment breakdowns
    28	- Generate Tikkie payment messages
    29	- Provide cost splitting results and summaries
    30	
    31	### Settings Storage
    32	- Store your preferences in Chrome's secure storage
    33	- Sync settings across your Chrome browsers (if Chrome sync is enabled)
    34	- Remember your Tikkie link for payment message generation
    35	
    36	## Data Security
    37	
    38	### Encryption
    39	- **Tikkie Links**: Encrypted using AES-GCM 256-bit encryption before storage
    40	- **Key Derivation**: PBKDF2 with 100,000 iterations
    41	- **Secure Storage**: All settings stored in Chrome's encrypted storage system
    42	
    43	### Security Measures
    44	- All data processing occurs locally in your browser
    45	- No external server communication for calculations
    46	- Tikkie links validated and sanitized before storage
    47	- Rate limiting to prevent abuse
    48	- Comprehensive input validation
    49	
    50	### Access Control
    51	- Only the extension can access stored settings
    52	- Tikkie links protected by encryption
    53	- No third-party access to your data
    54	
    55	## Data Sharing
    56	
    57	### We DO NOT Share Your Data
    58	- **No External Transmission**: Order data never leaves your browser
    59	- **No Analytics**: We don't collect usage analytics or tracking data
    60	- **No Third Parties**: Your information is never shared with external services
    61	- **No Advertising**: We don't use your data for advertising purposes
    62	
    63	### Chrome Sync (Optional)
    64	- If you enable Chrome sync, your encrypted settings may sync across your devices
    65	- This is handled entirely by Google Chrome's secure sync system
    66	- We have no access to your synced data
    67	
    68	## Data Retention
    69	
    70	### Temporary Data
    71	- **Order Information**: Processed temporarily and discarded after calculation
    72	- **No Persistent Storage**: Order data is never permanently stored
    73	
    74	### Settings Data
    75	- **User Preferences**: Stored until you uninstall the extension or clear them
    76	- **Automatic Cleanup**: Security logs automatically cleaned after 7 days
    77	- **User Control**: You can clear all settings at any time
    78	
    79	## Your Rights
    80	
    81	### Data Control
    82	- **Access**: View your stored settings in the extension popup
    83	- **Modify**: Change or update your settings at any time
    84	- **Delete**: Clear all settings or uninstall the extension to remove all data
    85	
    86	### Tikkie Link Management
    87	- **Update**: Change your Tikkie link at any time
    88	- **Remove**: Clear your Tikkie link to stop payment message generation
    89	- **Encryption**: Your link is always stored encrypted
    90	
    91	## Third-Party Services
    92	
    93	### Thuisbezorgd.nl
    94	- The extension reads order information from Thuisbezorgd.nl pages
    95	- We don't modify or interfere with Thuisbezorgd's functionality
    96	- No data is sent to Thuisbezorgd from our extension
    97	
    98	### Tikkie Integration
    99	- We only store your Tikkie link for message generation
   100	- No communication with Tikkie servers
   101	- Your Tikkie link is used only for creating payment messages
   102	
   103	## Children's Privacy
   104	
   105	This extension is not intended for use by children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
